properties.name: dialog
properties.value: Would you care to join me on a journey of intrigue?

properties.name: dialog
properties.value:
Now I myself am prone to traveling great distances, through time and space.

What say you to a long adventure?

properties.name: dialog
properties.value: We can just chill here then...

properties.name: dialog
properties.value:
I suppose we shall see how things unfold from here...

If you had to choose between losing a hand, and losing a foot, which would you lose?

properties.name: dialog
properties.value:
Cool, let's continue. Where would you rather see first?

(Don't worry, we can revisit different times, and different places easily enough).

properties.name: dialog
properties.value: You'd rather lose a hand hmm? Very interesting. I'm sure something can be arranged...

properties.name: dialog
properties.value: You'd rather lose a foot hmm? Very interesting. I'm sure something can be arranged...

properties.name: dialog
properties.value: A moonlit forest huh? Alright I'll bite.

properties.name: dialog
properties.value: Tropics huh? I don't care for the bugs, but I suppose we'll work it out.
